{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/01.gif?t=1740052552\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KILL. DIE. REBOOT.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s time for <strong>bravery, carnage, and adrenaline-fueled action</strong>. Welcome to <strong>DESPA </strong>\u2014 a no-nonsense, full-throttle <strong>first-person arena shooter</strong> where <strong>violence is the only language</strong> that matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s a <strong>post-cyberpunk Colosseum</strong> where <strong>androids battle </strong>for dominance in brutal, intensive showdowns. <strong>No fluff. No filler. Just you, your weapons, and the fight.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>METAL, SPARKS AND MAYHEM</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No-holds-barred combat </strong>in<strong> wrestling-style battles</strong> where every hit feels personal.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Post-cyberpunk fields </strong>are<strong> </strong>built for destruction.<strong> Fight. Dominate. Survive.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Arenas are designed for skill, </strong>not luck; master the battleground or be crushed.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>POST-CYBERPUNK SHOOTER\u2014PURE AND RAW</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No distractions. No hand-holding. <strong>Just war.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Brutal gunplay &amp; visceral melee combat: </strong>you feel every blow, every kill<strong>.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pure adrenaline. Harsh action. </strong>The arena shooter you crave.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>UNLEASH THE ULTIMATE ULTRAVIOLENCE</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No guilt. No rules.</strong> Just destruction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No morality. No consequences. </strong>Just pure mechanical carnage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Drench the world in machine oil because androids don\u2019t bleed.</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>THE SHOOTER YOU WERE MISSING</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic, relentless, and deadly: </strong>classic FPS energy supercharged for 2025.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Old-school skill, modern design, and raw intensity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every move counts \u2014 every shot matters.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>VICTORY THAT DEMANDS TO BE SEEN</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This isn\u2019t just a fight.<strong> It\u2019s a full-blown SHOW.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Winning means nothing if no one sees it. </strong>Make every moment legendary.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/extras/05.gif?t=1740052552\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ARE YOU READY TO FIGHT?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wishlist now! Don\u2019t just play. Dominate.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2259240?t=1740052552","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740052552","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/2311426af0ad32807bb825cfdf7a589aff90344a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740052552","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259240/2311426af0ad32807bb825cfdf7a589aff90344a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740052552","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"descript